    <tags>video-meeting webrtc self-hosted livekit desktop</tags>
    <summary>Native desktop client for the Bedrud self-hosted video meeting platform.</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
Bedrud Desktop is a native desktop client for the Bedrud video meeting platform.

Connect to your self-hosted Bedrud server for secure, private video meetings
powered by WebRTC and LiveKit. No data leaves your infrastructure.

## Features
- Connect to any self-hosted Bedrud server
- Supports multiple server instances
- Native performance via Rust + Slint UI
- Passkey / WebAuthn authentication

## Usage
After installing, launch Bedrud Desktop and point it at your Bedrud server URL.
See https://themadorg.github.io/bedrud/ for self-hosting instructions.
    ]]></description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/themadorg/bedrud/releases/tag/v0.1.0</releaseNotes>
